Title: Checkmk Discovery: Fixed crash if a host has no data sources configured
Level: 1
Component: checks
Compatible: compat
Edition: cre
Version: 2.0.0i1
Date: 1568880170
Class: fix

If a host has no data sources and a service discovery is executed the error message
<tt>local variable 'host_sections' referenced before assignment</tt> was shown on
discovery page.
